      "title": "MODE SWITCHING GUIDE",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "=== LONG VIDEO WORKFLOW (20 sec @ 24fps = 481 frames) ===\n\nI2V MODE (default): Load start image -> generates video from it\n  Active: LoadImage(2), VACEFrame(30), VACEEncode(31)\n\nT2V MODE: Text only, no image input\n  Mute: LoadImage(2), VACEFrame(30). Disconnect input_frames/masks from VACEEncode\n\nV2V MODE: Transform reference video\n  Mute: LoadImage(2), VACEFrame(30). Unmute LoadVideo(1)\n  Connect LoadVideo output -> VACEEncode input_frames\n\nDURATION: Change num_frames in VACEFrame(30) + VACEEncode(31)\n  81=3.4s | 241=10s | 481=20s | 721=30s (at 24fps)\n\nRESOLUTION: Change width/height in VACEEncode(31)\n  832x480=16:9 | 480x832=9:16 | 608x1080=Reels"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 91,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [1280, 340],
      "size": [315, 130],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 16,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "CONTEXT WINDOWS",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Splits long video into 81-frame windows\nwith 16-frame overlap for smooth blending.\n\nPyramid fuse = smoother transitions\nLinear fuse = sharper transitions\n\nThis is what makes 20-30 sec videos possible!"
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    }
